author: gadams
msg: Removed MAC_GLYPH_NAMES. That array was supposed to represent the standard Macintosh ordering of glyphs in a TrueType font (it does NOT correspond to the MacRoman encoding). In addition to not really having any purpose outside a font library, some entries were incorrect.
